Publish & Promote your Medical Event on mConferences
The #1 App for Medical Conferences Worldwide, with a database of over 20.000 medical events and over 7.000 registered users!

TagME Chrome Extension allows you to submit your Medical event's information, with just a single click!

No need for time consuming data entry, Easy, Fast, Free Upload!
Simply:

1. Visit the website or webpage of the medical event you want to publish
2. Click on TagME extension and tag the webpage
The data of your event will be submitted, validated and then published on mConferences
